dataSource.staticValue: Confidential – Tyson Foods, Inc. Internal Use Only

dataItem.name: Total NS / Lb Variance
dataItem.expression: [Total NS / Lb Actual] - [Total NS / Lb Budget]

dataItem.name: Total EBIT / Lb Variance
dataItem.expression: [Total EBIT / Lb Actual] - [Total EBIT / Lb Budget]

dataItem.name: PrevQuarter
dataItem.expression: maximum(decode([Presentation].[Fact].[Current Fiscal Quarter], 'Y', [Presentation].[Fact].[Fiscal Quarter], null) for report)

reportVariable.name: v_negativeTotalNS/Lb Actual
reportVariable.reportExpression: if([q_Main].[Total NS / Lb Actual] >= 0) then 'POS' else 'NEG'

reportVariable.name: v_negativeTotalEBIT/Lb Actual
reportVariable.reportExpression: if([q_Main].[Total EBIT / Lb Actual] >= 0) then 'POS' else 'NEG'

reportVariable.name: v_negativeTotalNS/Lb Budget
reportVariable.reportExpression: if([q_Main].[Total NS / Lb Budget] >= 0) then 'POS' else 'NEG'

reportVariable.name: v_negativeTotalEBIT/Lb Budget
reportVariable.reportExpression: if([q_Main].[Total EBIT / Lb Budget] >= 0) then 'POS' else 'NEG'

reportVariable.reportExpression: if([q_Main].[Total NS / Lb Variance] >= 0) then 'POS' else 'NEG'
